Package edu.virginia.lib.ld2solr.spi

Types to implement to create steps in ld2solr workflow.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CacheLoader
    An Stage.Acceptor that takes RDF (packaged in Models) and loads it into a cache.
    Indexer<IndexerHead extends IndexingTransducer>
    An Indexer produces IndexerHeads from a particular store or source of Linked Data.
    IndexingTransducer
    An IndexingTransducer is moved in a path across an LDPath backend and executes a single indexing tranformation, producing a NamedFields as the result of each execution.
    OutputStage
    A Stage of workflow that generates OutputRecords.
    RecordSink
    Accepts OutputRecords and does something useful with them.
    RecordSink.RecordPersister
    A RecordSink that persists its inputs.
    Stage<Produces>
    A stage of workflow.
    Stage.Acceptor<Accepts,Produces>
    A stage of workflow that is not the first and therefore accepts tasks.
    TriplesRetriever
    Creates retrieval tasks from Resources.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractStage<T extends AbstractStage<T,Produces>,Produces>
